(477, 1, '2019-03-12 09:41:10', '2019-03-12 09:41:10', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Studying in the field information technology, we deserve to do the effective projects that tries to convert the world to the technological era. Everyone of us know that this is the field that makes the world efficient, fast and reliable. Then our group started thinking to do some useful and effective ideas in IT. In the present context, the situation of our country in IT was critical. The skilled people of this field have to do work under pressure and with minimum income and cost. So, we(Iceberg Technology Group) were worrying about the future and country’s situation in IT.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Leaving the desire of abroad study we (Youjan Katwal, Prajjwal Sharma, Suraj Luitel and Bijay Koirala) gathered and decided to establish the organization that focuses on extending, expanding, enhancing and promoting the business and organization. Many ups and downs arose in our way but also we never gave up. We are now at this stage just because of the hard effort, great devotion and deep sacrifice of our team. All it is possible is due to the effort of each one of us. It would have not been possible to establish and run smoothly in the absence of our single member. Beside this our family, friends and elders are equally responsible. Another important credits goes to Mr. Dawa Sherpa by giving the great advice and support. Lastly, we thank to all of the people that played the variety of role in various sector.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About Us', 'Studying in the field information technology, we deserve to do the effective projects that tries to convert the world to the technological era. Everyone of us know that this is the field that makes the world efficient, fast and reliable. Then our group started thinking to do some useful and effective ideas in IT. In the present context, the situation of our country in IT was critical. The skilled people of this field have to do work under pressure and with minimum income and cost. So, we(Iceberg Technology Group) were worrying about the future and country’s situation in IT.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '259-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-12 09:41:10', '2019-03-12 09:41:10', '', 259, 'http://localhost/iceberg/259-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
